          fruit. Enjoying Jumput Cempedak knows no time boundaries as it can be
          savored anytime. Jumput Cempedak remains delicious whether eaten cold
          or warm. This food is even more enjoyable when paired with hot coffee
          or tea. This culinary delight falls into the category of seasonal
          cakes, so anticipating its arrival is part of the sensation of
          enjoying it.
        </p>
