        <p class="text-home">
          "Rintak" is a typical snack from Bangka, belonging to the category of
          dry cakes. The flavor of rintak is almost similar to sago cakes. The
          sensation of hardness when bitten but melting and soft once it's in
          the mouth will make friends fall in love since the first bite.
        </p>
